Class PlayerChoicesDataStructure.Builder

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am33.model.card.PlayerChoicesDataStructure.Builder
Enclosing class:
PlayerChoicesDataStructure
public static class PlayerChoicesDataStructure.Builder extends Object
Builder class for constructing instances of PlayerChoicesDataStructure. This builder allows selective setting of various player choices during gameplay.
